(ns rams-ui.components.alert
  (:require [reagent.core :as r]
            [re-frame.core :refer [dispatch subscribe reg-event-db reg-sub]]
            [clojure.string :as cstr]
            [rams-ui.util :refer [gen-uuid rendering-id set-db-value
                                  set-value get-value get-db-value]]
            [reagent-material-ui.core.snackbar :refer [snackbar]]
            [reagent-material-ui.styles :refer [make-styles]]
            [reagent-material-ui.icons.close :as iclose]
            [reagent-material-ui.core.icon-button :refer [icon-button]]
            [reagent-material-ui.lab.alert :refer [alert]]
            [reagent-material-ui.core.button :refer [button]]
            [reagent-material-ui.core.typography :refer [typography]]))

(def ^:no-doc id (gen-uuid))

(def ^:no-doc use-styles
  (make-styles (fn [theme]
                 {:close {:padding ((:spacing theme) 0.5)}})))

(defn show-alert
  "helper function that allows to show an alert. Takes the following arguments

  - **config**: an optional hashmap identifying anything happening in the alert
  
    - **:actions**: an optional array of hashmaps identifying the buttons available to this alert. Each hashmap should be of the form
      ```
      {:label \"button label\"
       :color \"primary\" ; could be either primary or secondary
       :on-click (fn [] ...)
      }```
    - **:show-close?**: boolean to indicate if the close icon should be shown
    - **:type**: is an optional string indicating the severity of the alert. Potential values are \"error\" | \"success\" | \"warning\" | \"info\". If left nil then the notification is shown as a black box.
  - **message**: the string that would be shown in the box"
  ([message]
   (show-alert {} message))
  ([{:keys [actions show-close? type] :as config} message]
   (set-value id {:open? true
                  :actions actions
                  :type type
                  :show-close? show-close?
                  :message message}
              :persistent? true)))

(defn hide-alert []
  (set-value [id :open?] false :persistent? true))

(defn- alert-box-helper
  [{:keys [hide-after-ms show-close?
           position on-close]} state]
  (let [style (use-styles)]
    [snackbar (merge {:anchorOrigin (case position
                                   :top-right {:vertical "top"
                                               :horizontal "right"}
                                   :top-center {:vertical "top"
                                                :horizontal "center"}
                                   :top-left {:vertical "top"
                                              :horizontal "left"}
                                   :bottom-right {:vertical "bottom"
                                                  :horizontal "right"}
                                   :bottom-center {:vertical "bottom"
                                                   :horizontal "center"}
                                   :bottom-left {:vertical "bottom"
                                                 :horizontal "left"})
                   :open (:open? state)
                   :on-close (fn []
                               (hide-alert)
                               (when (fn? on-close)
                                 (on-close)))
                   :key (gen-uuid)}
                  (when (nil? (:type state))
                    {:message (:message state)})
                  (when (and hide-after-ms
                             (not= hide-after-ms 0))
                    {:auto-hide-duration hide-after-ms})
                  (when (or show-close? (:actions state))
                    {:action (r/as-element
                              [:<>
                               (when (:actions state)
                                 (for [action (:actions state)]
                                   [button  {:size "small"
                                             :color (if (:color action)
                                                      (:color action)
                                                      "secondary")
                                             :on-click (fn []
                                                         (hide-alert)
                                                         (:on-click action))}
                                    (:label action)]))
                               (when show-close?
                                 [icon-button {:class-name (:close style)
                                               :on-click hide-alert}
                                  [iclose/close]])])}))
     (when (:type state)
       [alert {:severity (:type state)}
        (:message state)])]))

(defn alert-box
  "draws a react component for alerts. Only one should be added per project. Takes the following kesy

  - **:hide-afer-ms**: is the number of milliseconds before the alert is autohidden
  - **:show-close?**: is boolean indicating if there should be a close icond
  - **:on-close**: is an optional function that will be called when the notification is hidden either automatically or by click
  - **:position**: is an optional keyword indicating where the alert should appear. Potential values are :top-left | :top-center | :top-right | :bottom-left | :bottom-center | :bottom-right. Default is :top-left"
  [{:keys [hide-after-ms show-close?
           position on-close]}]
  (let [state (get-value id :persistent? true)]
    [alert-box-helper @state]))
